                        <LineBreak/>
                        Copyright © 2022 Henrik Eliasson
                        <LineBreak/>
                        <LineBreak/>
                        Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining
                        <LineBreak/>
                        a copy of this software and associated documentation files
